  "text": "In particular, our framework proposes novel weighting strategies for the explored semantic graphs. These weights can further be used to filter on KS semantic features relevant to a Micropost. This feature selection strategy also largely differs from state-of-the-art feature selection techniques (Forman et al. [CITATION_1] ) used in text classification, as they typically make use of the scores obtained for the features based on the text content only (e.g. occurrences of a feature in training positive-and negativeclass training examples separately).",
